snippet.title: Cyber Shadow - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Only you can unlock the secrets to your clan's ancient powers in Cyber Shadow, the thrilling new Ninja Action game from Mechanical Head Studios and Yacht Club Games - creators of Shovel Knight.
 
Available soon on Nintendo Switch!

#NintendoSwitch #CyberShadow
